{"tid":801889,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"美劇《仁心仁術》女演員雲妮莎馬克斯 被警員開槍擊斃","createTime":"2018-09-01T04:34:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T09:48:28.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3b378cb6906dfa235387f1fc387605ec76c747ab","tid":801889,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T04:34:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/AKfQrfnZkWkcGbKrUlEw1w--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzUwO2g9NjAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/https://media.zenfs.com/creatr-images/GLB/2018-09-01/215d1f80-ad9a-11e8-b91f-3ff533efca53__2018090110581131075.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FAKfQrfnZkWkcGbKrUlEw1w--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzUwO2g9NjAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fcreatr-images%2FGLB%2F2018-09-01%2F215d1f80-ad9a-11e8-b91f-3ff533efca53__2018090110581131075.jpg&h=5cd623eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【星島日報報道】著名美國電視劇《仁心仁術》(ER)中擔任護士一角的墨西哥裔女演員雲妮莎馬克斯(Vanessa Marquez)，在加州寓所因用手槍形狀物件指向警員，被警員開槍擊斃。<br />\n<br />\n事發在當地星期四上午，當地警方指，接到屋主報警指馬克斯癲癇症發作，要求協助，3警員連同精神病護理員趕到場了解，但馬克斯情緒激動，安撫近1小時無果，形容馬克斯當時表現得極不合作，到下午2時，她取出手槍形物件指向警員，警員於是開槍將她打中，送院後死亡。警方事後檢查她的手槍，發現只是一支玩具槍。<br />\n<br />\n49歲的馬克斯在1994-1997年有份參演《仁心仁術》，飾演護士戈德曼(Wendy Goldman)一角。她的朋友指，馬克斯事前無任何情緒低落的徵兆。"},{"pid":"39526d7976a8fb738a7567d280b25326897b9b89","tid":801889,"uid":85461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T04:35:02.000Z","msg":"阿sir開槍唔駛你教"},{"pid":"7bdeaab36b349540a8e522066dcbfc8af1753e8c","tid":801889,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T18:11:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f6e328bbab1e9b429e9147278cf204d989963e6a","tid":801889,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T18:16:43.000Z","msg":"張相影到好似遺照咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fr